      <p class="bibcategory"><a name="Media"></a>Media Adaptations       <p class="bibsubcategory">Motion Pictures: 
      <ul type=square class="bibsubcatlist">
        <li><b><i><a href="http://us.imdb.com/Title?Firm,+The+(1993)">The 
